271	Belgium	decoupling of permanent residence and work permit	2003	Reform of the Belgian work permit regulations in July 2002, with effect from 1 April 2003 - simplifying administrative procedures and gave those entitled to a permanent residence permit the right to obtain paid employment without needing to have a work permit (de-coupling of work permit from permanent residence)	SOPEMI 2005: 163	Major change	National policy	Integration	Work visa/permit	All migrants	All foreign nationalities	N/A	Less restrictive		
