1403	Denmark	training for rejected asylum seekers ready to return	2007	In June 2007, new support measures were introduced for certain groups of rejected asylum seekers who cooperate on voluntary return - These may obtain, among other reintegration aid, six to nine months of education and vocational training in Denmark	SOPEMI 2008: 238	Fine-tuning change	National policy	Exit	Reintegration/return programmes	Refugees, asylum seekers and other vulnerable people	All foreign nationalities	N/A	Less restrictive		
