2822	Hungary	first migration strategy	2009	In April 2009 the Government adopted the 5 year Strategy of the Cooperation in the Area of Freedom, Security and Justice of the Republic of Hungary (Strategy) - this is the first officially adopted document which draws up guidelines and goals to be fulfilled in the field of migration, asylum and integration. > The 20-page document sets out clear goals on several fields from illegal immigration to visa policies and external policies as well.	EMN 2009: 7	N/A	N/A	Legal entry and stay	Action Plan, Strategy, Report	All migrants	All foreign nationalities	N/A	N/A		
