4207	Luxembourg	work permit given to asylum seekers from war region	1999	Grand-ducal regulation of 29 avril 1999 - grants asylum seekers from war regions a temporary work authorisation (AOT) for six months for a specific employer and job > Are eligible for this measure:  The Albanians from Kosovo who entered Luxembourg after 14 april 1999, asylum seekers from the Balkans which entered LX beofre 14 april 1999 but did not get the response to their asylum claim yet or were refused but cannot be sent back.	http://www.legilux.public.lu/rgl/1999/A/1171/1.pdf [accessed on 10.02.2014]	Mid-level change	National policy	Integration	Work visa/permit	Refugees, asylum seekers and other vulnerable people	Specific nationalities	Ex-Yougoslavia	Less restrictive		
