4377	Luxembourg	Ecomomic migration, Working holiday visa- agreement with Taiwan	2018	Working holiday visa- agreement with Taiwan, signed 21 August 2018 - allows 40 Luxembourgers and Taiwanese nationals between the ages of 18 and 30 to work, study and travel in the other country for a period of 12 months. People wishing to benefit from this agreement must have sufficient financial resources to meet their daily living expenses	EMN	Fine-tuning change	Multi- or bilateral policy	Legal entry and stay	Entry visa/stay permit	Specific categories	Specific nationalities	Taiwan	Less restrictive		
