4534	Malta	preliminary vulnerability assessment of all new applicants for international protection	2017	Introduction of a preliminary vulnerability assessment of all new applicants for international protection  This assessment is done by non-medical staff and is mainly based on obvious indicators of vulnerability and on the applicants own statements	EMN 2017 factsheet p.2	Fine-tuning change	National policy	Legal entry and stay	Entry visa/stay permit	Refugees, asylum seekers and other vulnerable people	All foreign nationalities	N/A	Less restrictive		
