5647	Romania	People entering Romania from the most affected countries had to quarantine for 14 days	2020	People entering Romania from the most affected countries had to quarantine for 14 days, while other people entering the country needed to self-isolate for 14 days (daily cross-border workers as well as individuals coming for installation/maintenance of medical, scientific, economical, defence, public order and national security domains equipment are exempted)	SOPEMI 2020 p.288	Minor change	National policy	Legal entry and stay	Entry visa/stay permit	All migrants	All foreign nationalities	N/A	More restrictive		
