5818	Slovakia	new institution to deal with migration and naturalisation - not created yet	2012	Act 404/2011 on Residence of Aliens came into effect in January 2012 - created a new Immigration and Naturalization Office of the Slovak Republic as the only institution responsible for migration issues, currently dealt with by different bodies (the Ministry of Interior, the Bureau of the Border and Aliens Police, the Ministry of Labour Social affairs and Family, and other state administrative bodies and local authorities) > In 2012, this has not been created yet.	SOPEMI 2010: 238; SOPEMI 2013: 292	N/A	N/A	Legal entry and stay	Institutional capacities	All migrants	All foreign nationalities	N/A	N/A		
