5838	Slovakia	Act 495/2013, in force since 1 January 2014   subsidiary protection	2014	Act 495/2013, in force since 1 January 2014  provided that in case the circumstances under which the subsidiary protection was granted changed, ceased to exist or changed in such way that there is no furrher need to provide such protection, the subsidiary protection shall be cancelled. This provision shall not apply if the foreigner granted subsidiary protection provides serious reasons based on previous serious harm due to which s/he refuses the protection of the state which is the foreigners country of origin	EMN p.46	Mid-level change	National policy	Legal entry and stay	Entry visa/stay permit	Refugees, asylum seekers and other vulnerable people	All foreign nationalities	N/A	More restrictive		
