6304	Spain	more rights to reunited family members	1996	Royal Decree 155/1996 from 2 February 1996 -  for the first time tackles the issue of family reunification and grants rights to the family members > It allowing the immigrant to launch the family reunification procedure (and not the family members as was the case previously) after one year of residence.	Kreienbrink 2004: 293	Major change	National policy	Legal entry and stay	Entry visa/stay permit	Family members	All foreign nationalities	N/A	Less restrictive		
