7500	United Kingdom	stricter labour market test for Tier 2	2009	Tougher requirements for Tier 2 - changes introduced in September introduce stricter labour market tests for skilled workers with a job offer, religious workers, athletes and intra company transferees > The measures double the time for which jobs must be advertised in Jobcentre Plus (to four weeks) and raise the salary threshold for qualification as a skilled worker from 17000 to 20000 GBP.	SOPEMI 2009	Fine-tuning change	National policy	Legal entry and stay	Work visa/permit	Skilled/high-skilled workers	All foreign nationalities	N/A	More restrictive		
